{"data":[{"name":"86:1","price":"क़सम है आकाश की तथा रात में प्रकट होने वाले की!","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلطَّارِقِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5932,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāi wal-ṭāriqi ","translations":["By the sky","and the night comer","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāi","wal-ṭāriqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3260],[2,3260,5165]]}},{"name":"86:2","price":"और तुम क्या जानो कि रात में प्रकट होने वाला क्या है?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلطَّارِقُ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5933,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā al-ṭāriqu ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","the night comer (is)","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","al-ṭāriqu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2160],[2,2160,3240],[3,3240,3350],[4,3350,5025]]}},{"name":"86:3","price":"वह चमकता हुआ सितारा है।","arabic":"ٱلنَّجۡمُ ٱلثَّاقِبُ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5934,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"al-najmu al-thāqibu ","translations":["(It is) the star","the piercing","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["al-najmu","al-thāqibu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1960],[2,1960,3575]]}},{"name":"86:4","price":"प्रत्येक प्राणी पर एक निरीक्षक नियुक्त है।[1]","arabic":"إِن كُلُّ نَفۡسٖ لَّمَّا عَلَيۡهَا حَافِظٞ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5935,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (1-4) इनमें आकाश के तारों को इस बात की गवाही में लाया गया है कि ब्रह्मांड की कोई ऐसी वस्तु नहीं है, जो एक रक्षक के बिना अपने स्थान पर स्थित रह सकती है, और वह रक्षक स्वयं अल्लाह है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"in kullu nafsin lammā ʿalayhā ḥāfiẓun ","translations":["Not","(is) every","soul","but","over it","(is) a protector","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["in","kullu","nafsin","lammā","ʿalayhā","ḥāfiẓun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,900],[2,900,1730],[3,1730,2480],[4,2480,4350],[5,4350,5430],[6,5430,6875]]}},{"name":"86:5","price":"अतः इनसान को देखना चाहिए कि वह किस चीज़ से पैदा किया गया है?","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مِمَّ خُلِقَ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5936,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"falyanẓuri al-insānu mimma khuliqa ","translations":["So let see","man","from what","he is created","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["falyanẓuri","al-insānu","mimma","khuliqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2140],[2,2140,4160],[3,4160,5680],[4,5680,6905]]}},{"name":"86:6","price":"वह एक उछलने वाले पानी से पैदा किया गया है।","arabic":"خُلِقَ مِن مَّآءٖ دَافِقٖ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5937,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"khuliqa min māin dāfiqin ","translations":["He is created","from","a water","ejected","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["khuliqa","min","māin","dāfiqin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,710],[2,710,980],[3,980,4820],[4,4820,6045]]}},{"name":"86:7","price":"जो पीठ और सीने की हड्डियों के बीच से निकलता है।","arabic":"يَخۡرُجُ مِنۢ بَيۡنِ ٱلصُّلۡبِ وَٱلتَّرَآئِبِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5938,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"yakhruju min bayni al-ṣul'bi wal-tarāibi ","translations":["Coming forth","from","between","the backbone","and the ribs","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["yakhruju","min","bayni","al-ṣul'bi","wal-tarāibi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,1990],[3,1990,2670],[4,2670,3570],[5,3570,7365]]}},{"name":"86:8","price":"निःसंदेह वह उसे लौटाने में निश्चय सक्षम है।[2]","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ رَجۡعِهِۦ لَقَادِرٞ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5939,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. (5-8) इन आयतों में इनसान का ध्यान उसके अस्तित्व की ओर आकर्षित किया गया है कि वह विचार तो करे कि कैसे पैदा किया गया है वीर्य से? फिर उसकी निरंतर रक्षा कर रहा है। फिर वही उसे मृत्यु के पश्चात पुनः पैदा करने की शक्ति भी रखता है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu ʿalā rajʿihi laqādirun ","translations":["Indeed, He","to","return him","(is) Able","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","ʿalā","rajʿihi","laqādirun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,2590],[3,2590,3710],[4,3710,5275]]}},{"name":"86:9","price":"जिस दिन छिपी हुई बातों की जाँच-पड़ताल की जाएगी।","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تُبۡلَى ٱلسَّرَآئِرُ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5940,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma tub'lā al-sarāiru ","translations":["(The) Day","will be tested","the secrets","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","tub'lā","al-sarāiru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,560],[2,560,1270],[3,1270,4445]]}},{"name":"86:10","price":"तो (उस दिन) उसके पास न कोई शक्ति होगी और न ही कोई सहायक।[3]","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُۥ مِن قُوَّةٖ وَلَا نَاصِرٖ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5941,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3. (9-10) इन आयतों में यह बताया गया है कि फिर से पैदाइश इसलिए होगी ताकि इनसान के सभी भेदों की जाँच की जाए, जिनपर संसार में पर्दा पड़ा रह गया था और सबका बदला न्याय के साथ दिया जाए।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"famā lahu min quwwatin walā nāṣirin ","translations":["Then not","(is) for him","any","power","and not","any helper","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["famā","lahu","min","quwwatin","walā","nāṣirin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1210],[3,1210,2560],[4,2560,4300],[5,4300,4890],[6,4890,6385]]}},{"name":"86:11","price":"क़सम है बार-बार बारिश बरसाने वाले आसमान की।","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلرَّجۡعِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5942,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāi dhāti al-rajʿi ","translations":["By the sky","which","returns","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāi","dhāti","al-rajʿi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2680],[2,2680,3300],[3,3300,4725]]}},{"name":"86:12","price":"तथा फटने वाली धरती की।","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ ذَاتِ ٱلصَّدۡعِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5943,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-arḍi dhāti al-ṣadʿi ","translations":["And the earth","which","cracks open","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-arḍi","dhāti","al-ṣadʿi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1730],[3,1730,3085]]}},{"name":"86:13","price":"निश्चय ही यह (क़ुरआन) एक निर्णायक कथन है।","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلٞ فَصۡلٞ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5944,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu laqawlun faṣlun ","translations":["Indeed, it","(is) surely a Word","decisive","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","laqawlun","faṣlun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1820],[2,1820,3720],[3,3720,4655]]}},{"name":"86:14","price":"और यह हँसी-मज़ाक़ नही है।[4]","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِٱلۡهَزۡلِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5945,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"4. (11-14) इन आयतों में बताया गया है कि आकाश से वर्षा का होना तथा धरती से पेड़ पौधों का उपजना कोई खेल नहीं, एक गंभीर कर्म है। इसी प्रकार क़ुरआन में जो तथ्य बताए गए हैं, वे भी हँसी-उपहास नहीं हैं, पक्की और अडिग बातें हैं। काफ़िर (विश्वासहीन) इस भ्रम में न रहें कि उनकी चालें इस क़ुरआन के आमंत्रण को विफल कर देंगी। अल्लाह भी एक उपाय में लगा है जिसके आगे इनकी चालें धरी रह जाएँगी।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā huwa bil-hazli ","translations":["And not","it","(is) for amusement","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","huwa","bil-hazli",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,670],[2,670,1080],[3,1080,2185]]}},{"name":"86:15","price":"निःसंदेह वे गुप्त उपाय करते हैं।","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَكِيدُونَ كَيۡدٗا","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5946,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"innahum yakīdūna kaydan ","translations":["Indeed, they","are plotting","a plot","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["innahum","yakīdūna","kaydan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,3230],[3,3230,4255]]}},{"name":"86:16","price":"और मैं भी गुप्त उपाय करता हूँ।","arabic":"وَأَكِيدُ كَيۡدٗا","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5947,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akīdu kaydan ","translations":["But I am planning","a plan","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akīdu","kaydan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,2235]]}},{"name":"86:17","price":"अतः काफ़िरों को मोहलत दे दें, उन्हें थोड़ी देर के लिए छोड़ दें।[5]","arabic":"فَمَهِّلِ ٱلۡكَٰفِرِينَ أَمۡهِلۡهُمۡ رُوَيۡدَۢا","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5948,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"5. (15-17) इन आयतों में नबी (सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम) को सांत्वना तथा अधर्मियों को यह धमकी देकर बात पूरी कर दी गई है कि आप तनिक सहन करें और विश्वासहीन को मनमानी कर लेने दें, कुछ ही देर होगी कि इन्हें अपने दुष्परिणाम का ज्ञान हो जाएगा। और इक्कीस वर्ष ही बीते थे कि पूरे मक्का और अरब द्वीप में इस्लाम का ध्वज लहराने लगा।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"famahhili al-kāfirīna amhil'hum ruwaydan ","translations":["So give respite","(to) the disbelievers","Give respite to them ","little","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["famahhili","al-kāfirīna","amhil'hum","ruwaydan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,2720],[3,2720,4210],[4,4210,6875]]}}],"chapter":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq","Chapter At-Tariq","Tariq","Surah Tariq","Chapter Tariq","At Tariq","Surah At Tariq","Chapter At Tariq","Surah 86","Chapter 86","The Morning Star","الطارق"],"version":{"key":"hindi_omari","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"hi","version":"1.1.4","last_update":1675069101,"title":"Hindi Translation","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Indian by Azizul-Haqq Al-Umary."}}